name: Roboto Factory - Part Six
description:
Friendly and relaxing meeting at Roboto Factory Inc.
Both the team of scientists and the workers are taking a week off in Cancun.
There will be anger management and leadership workshops, massages, card games, art therapy, soccer and tennis.
Given the surplus of sales of the Robotas and Robotos, it was decided to make this day of meeting between the different work teams to achieve a harmonious and productive climate to maintain production.
In a note to Forbes Norma Jara (prototype designer) commented: "Our commitment to our customers is our only priority".
ASCII ART Collectible By Roboto Factory inc.
